2011-11-09 | huang | v0.2 release

* library updated to latest stable release
* remove nodejs dependency
  use hunchentoot/hunchensocket/hunchen.io for HTTP/WebSocket server
* add new-project.sh
* cleanup load dependency mess
* server-side message type semantics change
  - event for async message, funcall for sync message
  - both event and funcall message handler must be registered (for security)
* add session information (use hunchentoot sessions)
* combine HTTP and WebSocket in the same port

